This is a '''list of international prime ministerial trips made by Jacinda Ardern''', the [[List of Prime Ministers of New Zealand|40th]] [[Prime Minister of New Zealand|Prime Minister]] of New Zealand. {{As of|November 2018}}, [[Jacinda Ardern]] has made eight international trips to twelve sovereign countries and two [[associated state]]s of New Zealand, since her premiership began on 26 October 2017.

